{
  "id": "5de216e0620f3300172273f3",
  "title": "現実よりも一拍遅くシャッターを切る",
  "created": 1575098092,
  "updated": 1575110471,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5de216e0620f3300172273f3",
      "text": "現実よりも一拍遅くシャッターを切る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098092,
      "updated": 1575098417
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ecaff09e00009dec69",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/adcb37026fbcc76f01c58ec0b4061f40]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098092,
      "updated": 1575098092
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ecaff09e00009dec6b",
      "text": "\t振り子が真下に来た瞬間を取るにはどうするかという話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098092,
      "updated": 1575098249
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ffaff09e00009dec6c",
      "text": "\t人間は見てからボタンを押す反応に遅れがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098111,
      "updated": 1575098276
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217a3aff09e00009dec79",
      "text": "\t\t「現実を見て光学カメラで撮る」場合と「デジタルカメラでモニターを見て撮る」場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098276,
      "updated": 1575098305
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217c0aff09e00009dec7b",
      "text": "\t\t\t振り子が真下に来たのを見てから押したのでは遅れてしまう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098305,
      "updated": 1575098318
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217c3aff09e00009dec7c",
      "text": "\t\t\tだから少し早く押す必要がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098307,
      "updated": 1575098319
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ffaff09e00009dec6d",
      "text": "\tデジタルカメラは人間よりも遅れている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098111,
      "updated": 1575098254
    },
    {
      "id": "5de2178daff09e00009dec78",
      "text": "\t\t「現実を見てデジタルカメラで撮る」場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098254,
      "updated": 1575098301
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217bcaff09e00009dec7a",
      "text": "\t\t\t真下に来たのを見てから押しても真下に来る前の画像が撮れる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098301,
      "updated": 1575098327
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217d7aff09e00009dec7d",
      "text": "\t\t\tこのシチュエーションでは少し遅く押す必要がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098327,
      "updated": 1575098327
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ffaff09e00009dec6e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t肌感として一拍遅らせる必要があると感じた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098111,
      "updated": 1575098339
    },
    {
      "id": "5de217e2aff09e00009dec7e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t250msなので良い近似だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098339,
      "updated": 1575098339
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24256aff09e0000299c5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109206,
      "updated": 1575109206
    },
    {
      "id": "5de216ffaff09e00009dec73",
      "text": "\tiPhone11ProMaxのカメラで動いてるブランコの最下点を撮影する練習 ([Facebook https://www.facebook.com/nishiohirokazu/posts/10219958183641482])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575098111,
      "updated": 1575109325
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24253aff09e0000299c5a",
      "text": "\t\t序盤は画面見て撮ってて、肉眼に切り替えたタイミングで全然映らなくなった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109203,
      "updated": 1575109325
    },
    {
      "id": "5de242e6aff09e0000299c60",
      "text": "\t\t\t「シャッターを押したタイミングより前の映像が撮れてるぞ？」という議論([Facebook https://www.facebook.com/nishiohirokazu/posts/10219958038997866])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109350,
      "updated": 1575109363
    },
    {
      "id": "5de242c1aff09e0000299c5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109313,
      "updated": 1575109313
    },
    {
      "id": "5de2432daff09e0000299c61",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109421,
      "updated": 1575109429
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24335aff09e0000299c63",
      "text": "\t[iPhone11ProMaxのカメラの解像度]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109429,
      "updated": 1575109430
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24335aff09e0000299c62",
      "text": "\t\tタイミングの身体感覚を訓練する気がない(機械にいい感じにしてほしい)場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109429,
      "updated": 1575109695
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24533aff09e0000299c69",
      "text": "\t\t\t画面を見ない or 構図だけ決めたら目を離す→タイミングは画面ではなく現実を見て決める",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109940,
      "updated": 1575109999
    },
    {
      "id": "5de2443daff09e0000299c65",
      "text": "\t\t\t解像度が大事ならバースト撮影(3024 × 4032, 100msec)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109693,
      "updated": 1575109762
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24447aff09e0000299c66",
      "text": "\t\t\tタイミングの一致度(時間軸方向の解像度)が大事なら4Kビデオ撮影(2160 × 3840, 33msec)を回す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109703,
      "updated": 1575110444
    },
    {
      "id": "5de24590aff09e0000299c6a",
      "text": "\t\t\tどちらの場合でも人間の反応速度を上回る感覚で撮影できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575110032,
      "updated": 1575110046
    },
    {
      "id": "5de2470eaff09e000016df56",
      "text": "\t\t\t　[https://gyazo.com/ed039a942fb56779fe9254bf8ca88799]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575110415,
      "updated": 1575110416
    },
    {
      "id": "5de2445caff09e0000299c67",
      "text": "\t\tいずれ解像度がもっと上がることで「全部ビデオでいい」って時代が来そう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109725,
      "updated": 1575109817
    },
    {
      "id": "5de244adaff09e0000299c68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575109806,
      "updated": 1575109806
    }
  ]
}